summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Webcrafters Studio AI code generation platform. Backend APIs are functional with AI generation working correctly (30-60 second generation time). Frontend authentication, navigation, and UI components are working well. Minor issues found with timeout handling and unauthorized response codes.
